134
The Fairy Crowning. Continued.
(Enter six Fairies, three at right and three at left. Running lightly in, they form a semi-circle facing before the throne in the
center. They salute the Queen as they enter by bowing very low. Play first strain of "Introduction" as the Fairies enter. The
Fairies should step four times for each measure, and thus keep exact time.)
Moderato.
